06:55.168 --> 07:10.887
think you look in the Scouts, something about 
discipline, and you look at possibility for

06:55.168 --> 07:10.887
leadership because you work your way up. and then 
also helping other people. And then you go back and

07:13.728 --> 07:15.651
you looked at A&M. I think if I'd been from a big city 
and had come down here, I don't know if I would have

07:16.973 --> 07:21.880
looked favorably on it. I looked at this as just 
kind of a neat experience because the bottom line,

07:29.227 --> 07:32.470
Everybody was basically the same in your class, 
you know.

07:35.773 --> 07:38.456
