16:05.503 --> 16:09.348
when you came to the campus to enroll, how did you 
get here? I got a ride with one of those six of us from

16:09.969 --> 16:15.055
Jacksboro, a gentleman named Bill Sparks. I 
remember it. very well. I had one footlocker. I got

16:18.512 --> 16:21.135
off over there in front of Dorm 2. That's Briggs 
Hall. And the guardroom, the Corps Staff

16:23.177 --> 16:26.540
guardroom was there. Put my footlocker down 
there. And all of a sudden, a guy named Bill Reagan

16:29.483 --> 16:39.874
was the first sergeant, this guy that looked very 
sharp and had khakis on starch. And he said,

16:39.894 --> 16:42.677
anybody here in A Veterinary Company? And And I was 
going to be in a veterinary company, so I got there

16:43.570 --> 16:49.478
just in time to leave my footlocker there. And I 
joined in, and we marched over to Sully. And as he

16:54.845 --> 16:59.231
said, we were the first unit in 58 to polish Sully. 
